headline: Fifth Third Bank, National Association, Names Scott Daigle as North Florida President, Cary Putrino as Region Chairman
summary: TAMPA, Fla., June 02, 2025--Fifth Third Bank, National Association, (Nasdaq: FITB) has announced Scott Daigle as North Florida region president. Daigle succeeds Cary Putrino, who has transitioned into a new role as region chairman in North Florida. Putrino will focus on business development, special projects and brand ambassadorship.
